OL,3,C'Immediate custody' for brothers who
OL,4,Clooted library during riots
OL,6,FTwo brothers who looted a community
OL,7,Fhub and library, which was set alight
OL,8,Fduring riots in the wake of the
OL,9,FSouthport knife attack, have been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FAdam Wharton, 28 and Ellis Wharton,
OL,13,F22, targeted the burnt-out site in
OL,14,FCounty Road, Walton, Liverpool, where
OL,15,Fwidespread public disorder took place
OL,16,Fearlier on Saturday August 3 as police
OL,17,Fofficers came under attack.
