OL,4,Clooted library during riots
OL,6,FAfter the disturbance subsided at
OL,7,Fabout 2am on 4 August, Adam Wharton
OL,8,Facted as lookout while his younger
OL,9,Fbrother entered the burnt-out Spellow
OL,10,FHub premises.
OL,12,FThe library housed a number of
OL,13,Fcommunity facilities including a food
OL,14,Fbank ` just a "stone's throw away"
OL,15,Ffrom their home.
OL,17,FA police officer entered the building
OL,18,Fand caught a masked Ellis Wharton in
OL,19,Fthe act of removing a large computer
OL,20,Fmonitor.
