OL,4,Clooted library during riots
OL,6,FJudge Neil Flewitt KC said he had "no
OL,7,Fdoubt" that Adam Wharton, who has a
OL,8,Fstring of convictions for dishonesty
OL,9,Fincluding burglary, had involved and
OL,10,Fencouraged his younger brother, with
OL,11,Fno previous convictions.
OL,13,FThe judge told the brothers that
OL,14,F"appropriate punishment could only be
OL,15,Fachieved by immediate custody".
