OL,6,FSentencing Adam Wharton to 20 months
OL,7,Fin jail and Ellis Wharton to 11 months
OL,8,Fin jail, the judge said: "The Spellow
OL,9,FHub was a valuable local resource and
OL,10,Fits loss will be felt deeply by the
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"Although your offending amounts in
OL,14,Flaw to the offence of burglary, your
OL,15,Fconduct is more commonly described as
OL,16,F'looting' ` a despicable crime in
OL,17,Fwhich the offender seeks to profit
OL,18,Ffrom the misery of others."
