OL,6,F"This should serve as a stark warning
OL,7,Fto anyone who chooses to take part in
OL,8,Fsuch abhorrent behaviour. You will be
OL,9,Fswiftly arrested and could end up in a
OL,10,Fjail cell for a considerable amount of
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"The investigation to identify anyone
OL,14,Fwho took part in the disorder
OL,15,Fcontinues and we have now made 44
OL,16,Farrests in total.
OL,18,F"This will only rise as a specialist
OL,19,Fteam reviews hundreds of hours of
OL,20,Ffootage taken of the incidents."
